                <head>Death of General Robert E. Lee</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper reports the sorrowful news that General Robert E. Lee passed away
                    yesterday morning. The columns of the paper are bordered in black.</summary>
                <note/>
