            <div type="a">
                <column>01</column>
                <head>Relief for the Virginia Sufferers</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The citizens of Baltimore, Philadelphia, and New York are organizing relief
                    for the sufferers of the Virginia flood. The mayor of New York called a public
                    meeting and the chamber of commerce of that city will make the first donation.</summary>
                <note/>
